Former BBNaija ‘Lockdown’ season 5 housemate, Kiddwaya has disclosed his preference in terms of a life partner. In a video during a live chat session with DJ Cuppy shared by Kiddwaya on his Instagram page, the billionaire son explained his kind of woman must be someone who possesses a big heart among other attributes. While Cuppy lamented about most guys not being attracted to girls with short hair, Kiddwaya revealed he is different as he loves women with short hair. “I like short hair women, I think it’s great”, he said.   My sister is adored more than me – DJ Cuppy     Life as a single mom, by Iyabo Ojo     How I dropped off Jenifa’s Diary series, by Toyo Baby   - Advertisement - When eventually quizzed about his kind of woman, the reality TV star said: “I want someone with a big heart. That’s the only big thing I need. “Personality too because she’s gonna be the mother of my child. So you need to have for me, a great heart, God-fearing. “And I think you need to have great physical awareness. Awareness of what’s happening in the world.”